### NOTE — apply only if your hero has a "Try it" CTA

This is a hint, not a guaranteed-applicable patch. The exact JSX in
`integrations.tsx` may differ. The intent is:

  Anywhere on the homepage where a CTA reads "Try it free", "Get started",
  or "Try the generator" and currently navigates to `/best-ai-art-generator`,
  change the link to `<a href="#try">…</a>` so it scrolls to the embedded
  HomeGenerator section instead of doing a full route change. Keep buttons
  that send users to dashboard/pricing/sign-in unchanged.

  CSS to enable smooth scrolling on the homepage (one-line change):

      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  Add this to `app/app.css` if it isn't already there.
